divs: Sighting DetailsMy friend was meeting her husband for work at Winchester Industrial Park, She thought she saw a plane coming toward her so she started taking pictures with her cell phone, then she thought the plane was crashing, because it was moving side to side like it was unstable,then it got real bright and stoped right over her and then disapeared I have 3 pictures that she took with her cell phone.. I would like to know if someone could tell me if they are real and what this object is ...It is realy weird looking!
Summary: My friend thought she was watching an airplane...she took 3 pictures on her cell phone and we would like some one to see this.
